  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Benefits & Perks:</p><p>* Competitive salary range: SGD 2,300 - 2,800 per month</p><p>* Annual leave and medical coverage</p><p>* Annual Wage Supplement (AWS)</p><p>* Opportunities for overtime and shift work</p><p>Job Summary:</p><p>We are seeking a dedicated Warehouse Assistant to join our team in Singapore. The ideal candidate will be responsible for various warehouse operations, including goods handling, forklift operation, and inventory management. This role is crucial in maintaining an efficient and safe warehouse environment.</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>* Receive, check, and unload incoming goods, ensuring accuracy and proper documentation</p><p>* Operate forklift (below 3 ton) to load, unload, move, and stack pallets safely and efficiently</p><p>* Pick, pack, label, and prepare goods for delivery according to company standards</p><p>* Perform regular stock takes and inventory checks, maintaining accurate records</p><p>* Assist with general warehouse duties and maintain cleanliness and safety standards</p><p>Job Requirements:</p><p>* Valid forklift license (≤3 ton, MOM/WSQ recognized) with basic warehouse experience preferred</p><p>* Physically fit and safety-conscious, able to handle heavy workload</p><p>* Basic computer knowledge for updating records and system entries</p><p>* Strong teamwork skills with ability to work independently when required</p><p>* Willingness to work overtime, shifts, or take on additional responsibilities as needed</p><p>Whatsapp or contact 88571530 to schedule interview.</p>",
